Description: I have for auction a lovely Lodis medium multi-use briefcase which has a pocket for a tablet 9 to 10 inches long and an area for your items that you would take in a briefcase or a handbag too. The bag is a pebbled leather in a beautiful color they call toffee. This is the Lauren medium versionin the Stephanie Under Lock & Key line of products. This bag is RFID protected and has several storage options. The outside tablet pocket has two zipper pulls and opens all the way, see photo # 3. The pocket on the front side has a leather pull which slides into a secure hardware tab, see photo #1. There are double handles making it easy to grab which have a 4 in drop and the shoulder/crossbodystrap has a 20 in drop with a shoulder pad for extra comfort, see photo # 9 with clip on hardware.The hardware and zippers are all in a polished golden finish for extra bling. The bag measures 13 in long by 9 in high and 4 in deep not counting the tablet pocket on the back side. The inside has a bronze textile lining with a zippered pocket on one side and a long slip pocketon the other side in the main area of this bag. Overall, this is a well made and useful item thatwill provide years of service. The bag comes with a dust/storage bag included. Payment is by Paypal only and due within 4 days from the end of the auction. I will ship within 2 daysfrom cleared payment by USPS with tracking. I do not ship outside the USA and there are some additional restrictions, please check the shipping information. My items are genuine as stated and purchased by me from major retailers. They are from both a smoke & pet free environment. I do not take returns, please be positive before you bid.Items have not been on display or handled in a store, they were removed from packing for pictures only. Thanks for looking and have a nice day!
